Representation of Qubits¶

1. Bloch Sphere
2. Dirac Notation
3. Matrix Representation
In [ ]:
import cirq
import numpy as np
import cirq_web.bloch_sphere as bloch_sphere
In [ ]:
vec = [1/np.sqrt(2),-1/np.sqrt(2)]

1. Bloch Sphere¶

In [ ]:
bloch_sphere.BlochSphere(3,vec) # 3 is radius and vec is the vectors
Out[ ]:

2. Dirac Notation¶

In [ ]:
cirq.dirac_notation(vec)
Out[ ]:
'0.71|0⟩ - 0.71|1⟩'

In [ ]:
